      <h5>Site Design</h5>
      <p>Dave Thomas and Andy Hunt hired me to create a template for their website <em>The Pragmatic Bookstore</em>. The site markets their books and screencasts to programmers and people involved with technology. Books are available in paper, PDF, or eBook format. <a href="http://pragprog.com">View&nbsp;Site&nbsp;&raquo;</a></p>
