      <h5>Site Design</h5>
      <p>After finishing <em>The Pragmatic Bookstore</em> site with Dave and Andy, I helped Mike Clark apply a similar look and feel to <em>The Pragmatic Studio</em> website. <em>The Pragmatic Studio</em> provides top developer training from the folks who wrote the books. <a href="http://pragstudio.com">View&nbsp;Site&nbsp;&raquo;</a></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
